  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"wordsection1\"><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">覆蓋區域：兩條肢體，或者胸膛，或者上背部</span></p><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"wordsection1\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">該魔法刺青用一根特殊的針製作，且其圖案特別突出了一種顏色。</span><br /><em><strong>刺青同調</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。同調此物品時，你需要將針持握，並抵在你想要讓刺</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">青出現</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">的那處面板上。當同調完成時，針頭會化為墨水再變成刺青。</span> <br /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">若你與刺青的同調結束，刺青會消失，針頭會再次出現在你的位置中。</span> <br /><em><strong>傷害抗性</strong></em> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。當刺青在你的面板上時，你擁有與刺青顏色相聯繫的一種傷害抗性，如下方表格所示。</span>DM<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">可以自己選擇或隨機決定刺青顏色。</span><br /><em><strong>傷害吸收</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。當你受到與刺青所選傷害種類一致的傷害時，你可以用你的反應獲得對該次傷害的免疫，而後你回覆等同於你原先要受到傷害數值一半的生命值。使用后，直到下次黎明前，這個反應不能再次使用。</span></p></div><table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"BORDER-COLLAPSE:collapse;mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184\" border=\"0\"><tbody><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes\"><td style=\"BORDER-TOP:medium none;BORDER-RIGHT:medium none;BORDER-BOTTOM:#8eaadb 1pt solid;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;PADDING-TOP:0cm;PADDING-LEFT:5.4pt;BORDER-LEFT:medium none;PADDING-RIGHT:5.4pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid #8EAADB .5pt;mso-border-bo